50|$|To {{the south}} {{east of the}} Homestead and {{connected}} to its verandah with a covered walkway, is a smaller timber building known as the Cottage. Encircling it are wide verandahs on all sides, with an infill section of the south east. This building is constructed of vertical slabs of timber housed in recessed timber sections {{at the top and}} base of the wall, and the building features a similar <b>double</b> <b>roof</b> system to that previously described. The verandah is supported on chamfered timber posts.|$|E
